ArchetypeGraph, Cloneable, DirectedGraph, Graph, UserDataContainer
public class DirectedSparseGraph
extends SparseGraph
implements DirectedGraph

An implementation of Graph that consists of a Vertex set and a DirectedEdge set. This implementation does NOT ALLOW parallel edges. SimpleDirectedSparseVertex is the most efficient vertex for this graph type.

Edge constraints imposed by this class: DIRECTED_EDGE, NOT_PARALLEL_EDGE

For additional system and user constraints defined for this class, see the superclasses of this class.

Author:
Scott D. White, Danyel Fisher, Joshua O'Madadhain
See Also:
DirectedSparseVertex, DirectedSparseEdge
